name: SimpsonsSpeak
0:
”Alexa, tell Simpson Speak to give me a quote”
”Alexa, tell Simpson Speak to give me a Simpsons quote”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: simpson speak
des:
This skill is based on the classic, iconic TV show "The Simpsons".
With help from a Simpsons Quote API by Jason Luboff, this skill generates a random fact from one of the hilarious characters from the show.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
